text: "Invincible" is a 1985 Grammy nominated lead single from Pat Benatar sixth studio album Seven the Hard Way. It was used in the 1985 movie The Legend of Billie Jean. It went to number 6 in Canada, number 9 in Belgium, number 10 in the United States, number 18 in the Netherlands and number 23 in Australia.
